    <p>SPH Reit non-ex­ec­u­tive di­rec­tor David Chia Chay Poh, 65, has re­signed to pave the way for the “re­newal of board mem­bers”.</p>
    <p>His res­ig­na­tion is ef­fec­tive from Dec 1. He has been a non-ex­ec­u­tive di­rec­tor since June 10, 2013, a mem­ber of the au­dit and risk com­mit­tee, as well as chair­man of the nom­i­nat­ing and re­mu­ner­a­tion com­mit­tee. He di­rectly holds 150,000 units in SPH Reit.</p>
    <p>Mrs Trina Loh, 61, has been ap­pointed as non-ex­ec­u­tive di­rec­tor, and will take over Mr Chia’s com­mit­tee roles. Her ap­point­ments take ef­fect from Dec 1 as well.</p>


